<Layout title="eCommerce Website" description="Looking for a powerful, affordable ecommerce website in Auckland? Kiwi Web Design builds secure, mobile-friendly online stores with fast turnaround and local support." schema={schema}>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">eCommerce</p>
        <h1>eCommerce Website Design</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Looking for a powerful, affordable ecommerce website in Auckland? Kiwi Web Design builds secure, mobile-friendly online stores with fast turnaround and local support.</p>
        <div class="hero-btns">
          <a href="/website-designer-auckland/#contact" class="btn-primary">Book Free Consultation</a>
          <a href="/small-business-website-design-auckland/#packages" class="btn-outline">View Packages</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-img">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1688561808434-886a6dd97b8c?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;q=80&amp;w=800&amp;ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MXxhbGx8fHx8fHx8fHwxNzU5OTU3MDY5fA&amp;ixlib=rb-4.1.0" alt="eCommerce Website Design" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="prose">
<h4>Affordable online store solutions

</h4> 

 

<p>Selling online should be simple, effective, and <a href="/affordable-web-design-auckland/">affordable</a>. At Kiwi Web Design, we build eCommerce websites that make it easy for your customers to browse, buy, and come back for more. See <a href="/affordable-web-design-auckland/website-cost-new-zealand-small-business/">how much it costs</a> here.</p> 

