 <h3>Local setup done right</h3>
 <p>We configure <a href="https://www.ird.govt.nz/gst">GST</a>, NZ shipping zones, and payment gateways so your checkout meets Auckland customer expectations from day one.</p>

<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="presentation" aria-hidden="true">
 <path d="M5 12l4 4 10-10" stroke="#000" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
 </svg>
 
 <h3>Conversion focused</h3>
 <p>Lean <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/UXDesign/">UX</a>, speedy page loads, and pared-back checkout steps help shoppers add to cart and complete their order without friction.</p>

<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="presentation" aria-hidden="true">
 <path d="M8 8h8M8 12h5M6 4h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12l-4-3-4 3-4-3-4 3V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2z" stroke="#000" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
 </svg>
 
 <h3>Owner friendly</h3>
 <p>We leave you with product editing guides and team training so you can update inventory, imagery, and promos without waiting on support.</p>

<h3>Our process</h3>
 <p>Clear milestones keep your launch predictable and collaborative.</p>

<strong>1. Plan</strong>
 <p>We map audience goals, product priorities, and the integrations that will streamline operations.</p>

<strong>2. Build</strong>
 <p>Design and develop the storefront theme with accessible navigation and mobile-first layouts.</p>

<strong>3. Populate</strong>
 <p>Content, imagery, and collections are loaded with tidy metadata and smart product structures.</p>

<strong>4. Launch</strong>
 <p>We test payments, fulfilment, and analytics so you can go live knowing every workflow connects.</p>

<h3>Everything your store needs</h3>
 <ul>
 <li><a href="https://woocommerce.com/">WooCommerce</a> or Shopify guidance tailored to your niche</li>

 <li>Click &amp; collect and delivery options ready for local shoppers</li>
 <li>NZ tax and GST configuration without the guesswork</li>
 <li>Payment gateways including Stripe, PayPal, and invoicing on order</li>
 <li>Product variations, bundles, and flexible shipping rules</li>
 <li>Analytics and tracking setup aligned with your marketing</li>
 </ul>

<h3>Built for Auckland growth</h3>
 <p>Our ecommerce web design Auckland team keeps your voice local while delivering online store development in Auckland that converts browsers into loyal customers and supports long-term retail growth.</p>
